These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg, go
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, blend, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, pop, hip-hop, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the siglo-smoker##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game    | backgammon  | go | mah-jongg    | monopoly       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | bongani    | blend      | siglo |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | hip-hop | pop | classical        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, light-blue, coral, turquise
House: farmhouse, craftsman, tower, modern
City: london, hannover, boston, liverpool
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to london is the farmhouse house##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Color        | coral   | light-blue | mauve     | turquise      |
| House         | craftsman | tower | modern | farmhouse |
| City   | hannover    | liverpool   | boston     | london      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, milkpy, orchid
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk, milk
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, billiard, backgammon
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growsmilkpy##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsorchid is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Flower         | daisy | dahlia | milkpy | orchid |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda    | 7up | soy-milk     |
| Game   | canasta | billiard    | backgammon | snooker    |

