.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
City: prague, marseilles, london, hamburg
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, fishing, cooking, board-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, coffee, tea
1. the person traveling to london is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is the person traveling to london##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| City         | prague | hamburg | london | marseilles |
| Hobby       | fishing     | board-games      | baking     | cooking      |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate         | tea      | coffee        |

