.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
City: boston, berlin, venice, rome
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, pall-mall, ritmeester
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the game-smoker is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the person traveling to rome is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| City         | venice   | rome | berlin  | boston      |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | helicopter        | scooter  | motorbike       |
| Cigar         | game | pall-mall    | aristoff | ritmeester |

