.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, argentine, thai, british
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, card-games, traveling, sudoku
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, colonial, farmhouse
1. the turkish is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the british##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
5. the argentine is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the thai##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the british is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality           | argentine | thai | british | turkish |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | traveling  | card-games | filmmaking   |
| House   | farmhouse   | craftsman     | colonial | gothic-revival       |

