.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, dog, mouse, goat
House: cottage, modern, victorian, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, australian, turkish, indian
1. the victorian house is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the australian##1
4. the australian is the owner of the mouse##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the turkish is on the left of the brazilian##1
7. the cottage house is on the right of the modern house##1
8. the modern house is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Pet          | snake  | goat | mouse   | dog     |
| House         | tower | modern   | cottage  | victorian |
| Nationality   | turkish         | brazilian  | australian | indian  |

