.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, february, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, yellow, emerald
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, fonseca, siglo
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the siglo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | december | february     | january | august |
| Color   | emerald  | fuchsia | yellow       | orange    |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | siglo | dannemann    | fonseca |

