4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

