.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, daffodil, azalea
4 different games are played: snooker, go, canasta, mah-jongg
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, blueberry, carrot, apple
1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
7. the person playing snooker is the person eating carrot##1
8. the person playing canasta is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Flower         | amaryllis  | azalea | balloon-flower  | daffodil |
| Game       | canasta | go        | mah-jongg | snooker       |
| Food   | kiwi   | blueberry          | apple          | carrot       |

