.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, journalist, freelancer, engineer
4 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, horse, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, snowboarding, rugby
1. the chef is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the cat is the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the freelancer is on the right of the engineer##1
6. the chef is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | engineer   | freelancer   | chef | journalist |
| Pet   | horse | turtle | ferret   | cat |
| Sport   | rugby     | baseball  | snowboarding  | badminton  |

