.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, red, turquise, blood-red
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, pepper, spinach, grapefruit
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, sports, scientific, fantasy
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Color         | blood-red | red    | orange        | turquise |
| Food   | pepper     | spinach     | grapefruit        | zucchini   |
| Movie-Genre         | sports   | superhero | scientific | fantasy  |

