.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, badminton, skiing, ice-hockey
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, fish, hamster
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, domino, billiard
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | badminton   | ice-hockey  | climbing    | skiing    |
| Pet   | hamster | fish  | lizard  | snake |
| Game     | billiard  | backgammon | domino | go        |

