.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, goat, rat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, soul, rock, dubstep
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia, zinnia, sunflower
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
4. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
5. the fan of disco is the person who growszinnia##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Pet           | lizard  | goat  | ferret | rat |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | disco | soul   | rock      |
| Flower         | poppy | zinnia    | dahlia   | sunflower         |

 